{"tid":1860644,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國內地交通部門要求湖北以外省做好防疫有序逐漸恢復運輸，疫情完了準時返工共產黨奴隸","createTime":"2020-02-03T18:46:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T19:30:59.000Z","uid":125193,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"61b043ec561a70f0d6985bdb051eb4371e03efe6","tid":1860644,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T18:46:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1506456-20200204.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1506456-20200204.htm&d=oexceJgjEuhZ1NUs%2FbcNdKQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=03fdcb36\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1506456-20200204.htm&h=b2f73eae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1506456-20200204.htm</a>"},{"pid":"804b394efbec0835633b64417fabb0ef87d94163","tid":1860644,"uid":125193,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T18:47:05.000Z","msg":"中國交通運輸部等部門聯合印發通知，要求對湖北省以外其他地區，在做好疫情防控工作前提下，應結合復工開學時間安排，有序逐漸恢復已暫停運營的交通運輸服務。<br />\n<br />\n通知指出，各地交通運輸部門要指導交通運輸經營者統籌運力安排，合理優化運營班次，為乘客隔位、分散就座以及在交通運輸工具內，設置途中留觀區域創造條件。<br />\n<br />\n通知要求，嚴格規範和加強乘客測溫工作，對體溫超過攝氏37.3度的乘客，要按照程序第一時間移交衛生健康部門。"},{"pid":"f01ac1e1218b193342bcf9484bd7688c235e08e7","tid":1860644,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T18:47:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"726d1f6bd283245294d76476edeb6c959f54ffc6","tid":1860644,"uid":144626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T18:48:06.000Z","msg":"痴撚線，廣東疫情爆緊仲要復工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji